{"tid":582634,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"買股票有既權 voting rights","createTime":"2018-03-06T10:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T10:13:17.000Z","uid":133875,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"424a8ea616b4f8c64d181037c6a36a5b8fea935d","tid":582634,"uid":133875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:48:05.000Z","msg":"想同大家分享一下你買股票既權<br />\n<br />\n美國股市已經有啲係有股票冇投票權<br />\n<br />\n同埋有好多指數如sp 500 係唔俾冇投票權既股入場<br />\n<br />\n所以如果你見到啲大型股冇係指數入面，咁最好要注意下<br />\n<br />\n事關間公司既運行全部係內定<br />\n<br />\n例1. Snap <br />\n<br />\n例2. swch - 依間ipo 時紅咗1日，問題係佢出既share class，冇乜股權重要你買既股只得12.6% economic interest ，姐係你1股只可以得到12.6%佢本身公司1股利益<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港市場都開始睇weighted voting right structure <br />\n以後有可能會俾依種公司上ipo<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以大家買股時要注意一下"},{"pid":"46c571e6cd4f4e37bf65494b0b515e884d3c5eb7","tid":582634,"uid":10079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:53:42.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fc8eb52fc06b01724124ee8d612a380c4a4bfee7","tid":582634,"uid":37631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:56:00.000Z","msg":"以為係有權食盤菜post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651279fc799137f57ac8fe3fbe82cf12f5d66afd","tid":582634,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:10:50.000Z","msg":"唔同class 嘅股票係咪有利公司長遠發展?<br />\n之前上堂聽過美國好多科技公司都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過香港班仆街一定拎黎玩財技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff97b5e2522671fea9fb79cf2ee8b6318ca9a00","tid":582634,"uid":63302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:17:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49b61e79593924f980d3ce4f5c9a3be4b825f085","tid":582634,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:13:17.000Z","msg":"香港不嬲都存在同股不同權"}]}